parameters: "Once upon a time, this village was very peaceful, but because of the greed of our tribal chief, most of this village was turned into a barren land"
"and some of the villagers were turned into living skeletons"
"even so we still keep a treasure in a pyramid"
"Whoever goes there and opens it will have good luck wherever he goes"
"but be careful, some villages are cursed in other ways"
